long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Experience the intense aura of Overwatch’s Genji every time you open a new tab. Our Chrome extension offers a striking Genji live wallpaper that breathes life into your browser with every refresh. Enjoy a sleek, minimalist interface that blends perfectly with any browsing setup, bringing chrome wallpaper enthusiasts a new level of visual appeal.

This chrome background extension features everything you need for an immersive experience:

Live Wallpaper: Captures Genji’s action-packed energy
Google Search Bar: Integrated for quick access to your searches
Customizable Shortcuts: Add or remove site shortcuts with ease
Clock and Date Display: Keep track of time in style

Ideal for chrome live wallpapers fans, this extension not only brings you a character you love but also enhances productivity with essential features in a seamless design.
